We professionally provide various accessories for domestic servo motors and PLCs from manufacturers such as Mitsubishi, Yaskawa, Delta, Panasonic, Omron, and Siemens, including connection cables and connectors. These accessories mainly include servo encoders, power cables, control connectors, power aviation plugs, terminal blocks and cables, lithium batteries, PLC program download cables, and connection wires. We also offer brake resistors and fieldbus systems, as well as a wide range of electrical wires and cables. All accessories are manufactured in strict accordance with Mitsubishi standards and are custom-made by professional engineers.
